  "htmlSrcdoc": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Security-Policy\" content=\"default-src 'none'; base-uri 'none'; style-src 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'unsafe-inline'; img-src data:; font-src data:;\">\n<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { background: #F7F8FA; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; padding: 28px 24px; }\n  h1 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #94A3B8; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n  .subtitle { font-size: 12px; color: #94A3B8; margin-bottom: 28px; }\n  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }\n  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; border: 1px solid #E8EDF2; }\n  .card-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #94A3B8; margin-bottom: 18px; }\n  .logo-area { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; }\n  /* Dark bg variant */\n  .logo-dark { background: #0F172A; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; }\n  .logo-light { background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; border: 1px solid #E8EDF2; }\n  .desc { font-size: 12px; color: #64748B; line-height: 1.6; }\n  .tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; background: #F0FDF4; color: #16A34A; border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n\n  /* === CONCEPT A: Pulse waveform dot === */\n  .a-mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px; margin-right: 10px; }\n  .a-bar { width: 3px; border-radius: 2px; background: #10B981; }\n  .a-text { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }\n  .a-text .pp { color: #fff; }\n  .a-text .pulse-accent { color: #10B981; }\n  .a-text-dark .pp { color: #0F172A; }\n  .a-text-dark .pulse-accent { color: #10B981; }\n\n  /* === CONCEPT B: Chart upward triangle === */\n  .b-mark { width: 28px; height: 28px; margin-right: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }\n  .b-text { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }\n  .b-pp-dark { color: #fff; }\n  .b-pp-light { color: #1E293B; }\n  .b-sub { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #64748B; display: block; margin-top: -2px; }\n  .b-sub-light { color: #94A3B8; }\n\n  /* === CONCEPT C: Stethoscope + circuit === */\n  .c-mark { width: 30px; height: 30px; margin-right: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }\n  .c-text { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }\n  .c-pp-dark { color: #fff; }\n  .c-pp-light { color: #1E293B; }\n  .c-dot { color: #6366F1; }\n\n  /* === CONCEPT D: Abstract P monogram === */\n  .d-mark { width: 34px; height: 34px; margin-right: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }\n  .d-text { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }\n  .d-pp-dark { color: #fff; }\n  .d-pp-light { color: #0F172A; }\n  .d-accent { color: #F59E0B; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h1>PraxisPulse \u2014 Logo Directions</h1>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">4 distinct directions \u00b7 dark + light variants</p>\n\n<div class=\"grid\">\n\n  <!-- CONCEPT A -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-label\">Direction A \u2014 Pulse Bars</div>\n    <div class=\"logo-area\">\n      <!-- Dark -->\n      <div class=\"logo-dark\">\n        <div class=\"a-mark\">\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:18px\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:12px\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:24px\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:14px\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"a-text\"><span class=\"pp\">Praxis</span><span class=\"pulse-accent\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <!-- Light -->\n      <div class=\"logo-light\">\n        <div class=\"a-mark\">\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:8px;background:#CBD5E1\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:18px;background:#CBD5E1\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:12px;background:#10B981\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:24px;background:#10B981\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:14px;background:#CBD5E1\"></div>\n          <div class=\"a-bar\" style=\"height:8px;background:#CBD5E1\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"a-text a-text-dark\"><span class=\"pp\">Praxis</span><span class=\"pulse-accent\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"tag\">Recommended</span>\n    <p class=\"desc\">The bars read as both a revenue/analytics chart <em>and</em> a heartbeat monitor. \"Pulse\" feels alive. Works at small size. Teal (#10B981) signals health without being clinical red. Strong for favicon \u2014 just the bars.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CONCEPT B -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-label\">Direction B \u2014 Wordmark + Tagline</div>\n    <div class=\"logo-area\">\n      <!-- Dark -->\n      <div class=\"logo-dark\">\n        <svg class=\"b-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\">\n          <rect width=\"28\" height=\"28\" rx=\"7\" fill=\"#10B981\"/>\n          <polyline points=\"4,22 10,14 16,18 24,6\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"6\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"white\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"b-text b-pp-dark\">PraxisPulse</div>\n          <span class=\"b-sub\" style=\"color:#6EE7B7;\">AI for Clinic Doctors</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <!-- Light -->\n      <div class=\"logo-light\">\n        <svg class=\"b-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\">\n          <rect width=\"28\" height=\"28\" rx=\"7\" fill=\"#0F172A\"/>\n          <polyline points=\"4,22 10,14 16,18 24,6\" stroke=\"#10B981\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"6\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#10B981\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"b-text b-pp-light\">PraxisPulse</div>\n          <span class=\"b-sub b-sub-light\">AI for Clinic Doctors</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"desc\">Icon is a rising trend line inside a rounded square \u2014 the language of finance dashboards and analytics apps. Immediately communicates \"business intelligence.\" Tagline anchors the audience. App-icon ready.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CONCEPT C -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-label\">Direction C \u2014 Stethoscope + Data</div>\n    <div class=\"logo-area\">\n      <!-- Dark -->\n      <div class=\"logo-dark\">\n        <svg class=\"c-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 30\" fill=\"none\">\n          <circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"15\" r=\"13\" stroke=\"#6366F1\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n          <path d=\"M9 10 Q9 16 15 16 Q21 16 21 10\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          <line x1=\"15\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"21\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"22\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#6366F1\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div class=\"c-text c-pp-dark\">Praxis<span class=\"c-dot\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <!-- Light -->\n      <div class=\"logo-light\">\n        <svg class=\"c-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 30\" fill=\"none\">\n          <circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"15\" r=\"13\" stroke=\"#6366F1\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n          <path d=\"M9 10 Q9 16 15 16 Q21 16 21 10\" stroke=\"#1E293B\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          <line x1=\"15\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"21\" stroke=\"#1E293B\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"22\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#6366F1\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div class=\"c-text c-pp-light\">Praxis<span class=\"c-dot\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"desc\">Stethoscope inside a data circle \u2014 merges clinical identity with tech. The indigo accent separates it from green-heavy health brands. Doctors immediately recognise the symbol. Risk: can feel like a hospital app vs. a business tool.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CONCEPT D -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-label\">Direction D \u2014 Bold Monogram</div>\n    <div class=\"logo-area\">\n      <!-- Dark -->\n      <div class=\"logo-dark\">\n        <svg class=\"d-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 34 34\" fill=\"none\">\n          <rect width=\"34\" height=\"34\" rx=\"9\" fill=\"#F59E0B\"/>\n          <text x=\"17\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"22\" font-weight=\"900\" fill=\"#0F172A\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\">P</text>\n          <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"10\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#0F172A\"/>\n          <line x1=\"22\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"17\" stroke=\"#F59E0B\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div class=\"d-text d-pp-dark\">Praxis<span class=\"d-accent\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <!-- Light -->\n      <div class=\"logo-light\">\n        <svg class=\"d-mark\" viewBox=\"0 0 34 34\" fill=\"none\">\n          <rect width=\"34\" height=\"34\" rx=\"9\" fill=\"#0F172A\"/>\n          <text x=\"17\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"22\" font-weight=\"900\" fill=\"#F59E0B\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\">P</text>\n          <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"10\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#F59E0B\"/>\n          <line x1=\"22\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"17\" stroke=\"#0F172A\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <div class=\"d-text d-pp-light\">Praxis<span class=\"d-accent\">Pulse</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"desc\">Bold serif \"P\" on an amber tile \u2014 premium, confident, consultant-grade. Amber is the colour of financial dashboards (think Bloomberg). Breaks away from health-tech green/blue conventions deliberately. For a tool doctors take seriously.</p>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
